# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ComicK Revive — only source/code and build inputs are tracked.
# Everything else (build output, deps, local notes, archives) is ignored.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Dependencies
node_modules/

# Build output / packaged artifacts
dist/
release/
*.zip

# Local-only working dirs (not shipped to the public repo)
docs/
logs/
testing/
sharedL/
local/

# Tooling / binaries
*.exe

# AI assistant / editor scratch
CLAUDE.md
CLAUDE.local.md
.claude/
tmpclaude-*
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# OS junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
nul

# Secrets / environment
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
*.keystore
